        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 italic">Source: <a href="https://www.businessipswich.com.au/key-industries/manufacturing/" class="text-[#f97316] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Business Ipswich Manufacturing</a>, <a href="https://www.defenceindustries.qld.gov.au" class="text-[#f97316] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Defence Industries Queensland</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

