        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C2C3B] mb-2">Redbank Plains Industrial</h3>
          <p>Premier logistics and distribution location off the Ipswich Motorway, home to major facilities including Officeworks' regional distribution centre. We finance warehouse equipment, delivery vehicles, and facility expansions for businesses capitalising on this strategic location's motorway access and proximity to the Port of Brisbane.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C2C3B] mb-2">Swanbank Enterprise Park</h3>
          <p>The 130-hectare BrisWest development opposite Cunningham Highway provides direct access to major transport corridors. We support manufacturing and logistics businesses with equipment finance for factory machinery, warehouse automation, and commercial vehicle fleets serving this growing clean energy and industrial hub.</p>
        </div>

